    "We describe the assay protocols in detail in the Supplementary Data S1.",
    "We describe the results of the 22 experiments in Table 1.",
    "In 91% of the experiments, we identified singledose (SD) hits that were reconfirmed in dose-response (DR) experiments.",
    "The average target DR hit rate was 6.7% compared to 8.8% from the SD screens.",
    "Only 16 of the 22 projects were structurally enabled with X-ray crystallography; one used a cryo-EM structure, while five used homology models with an average sequence identity of 42% to their template protein."
